name: Kobi Kalderon
note:
Product: Venture Capital, Start-ups, Early Stage Funding, Technology Development, Business Development, Services for startups, Entrepreneurship, and Software Development
Target Audience: B2B, B2C.
Results of the meeting: The company specializing on acceleration program for Start-ups. They're offering to collaborate in the way of hiring our employees, and selling them to the companies they're already cooperating with. It might be any position we have, it's depends of the orders they will receive. For now, they seemed to be interested in Lead Generation Manager, about the model of work. Also Kobi wants to talk to Nico about the possible ways of cooperation.
Next Step: I will send a description of the Lead Generation process, website, presentation.
Next Contact Date: Thursday 13.05.21. At 15:00 (We are in the same time zone).
Gold Ventures Incubator - additional meeting.
http://www.gold-ventures.com/

Fresh results of the meeting: 
The company specializing on acceleration program for Start-ups. They're offering to collaborate in the way of hiring our employees, and selling them to the companies they're already cooperating with. They are interested in Lead Generation Manager. Also Kobi talked to Nico about the possible ways of cooperation. 

Next Step: We will have the additional meeting with CEO of the 8TEC Eng.&Dev. LTD company. 

Next Contact Date: We will decide it via mail.

RESULT
Company name: Gold Ventures Incubator
Company website: http://www.gold-ventures.com/

During this meeting, we explained how our lead generators work and how lead generators can help attract new customers for them. Also we answer all of their questions about results, commitments, budget, contract, what language they will communicate with our staff, and possibility to work for a part-time.

We need to send by email examples of promotions for other companies.  They want to receive references of another company.

Khrystyna: She works as a lead generation manager for 5 months. Her main task is to find a suitable client and to set up a call with him. She can search for up to 100 leads per day. Besides she can use CRM system such as Hubspot and arrange events with the help of Google Calendar. 

Tetiana: her previous working experience was as a sales manager both in restaurant and fashion spheres. So she answered calls, helped with the choice of goods and monitored payments.
Now she is working as a lead generation manager and reaches out to potential clients through LinkedIn.

Igor: His job responsibilities include searching for leads through LinkedIn, collecting databases, sending calls. He has good experience in CRM systems.
Igor also graduated from university as a custom specialist and during his university days, he was the student government council.
Moreover, he worked in Thailand as a real state sales manager and as a personal assistant within the first wave of the Covid outbreak.

Alina: She worked as a sales manager for 2 months and as a lead generation manager for 1 month. She has experience in finding leads from different industries such as the medical device area, online media, fashion, design, etc. Currently, she studies at university to become a translator. Thus her English speaking and writing skills are pretty decent. 

Kobi chooses Igor among other candidates as the most suitable employee for his project. He is willing to start a mutual job as soon as possible. Prefers for instant messaging WhatsApp.

name: Pete Howard
note:
Hi Alyona, I’d be interested in seeing whether this could work for us. Can you tell me more?
Hi Alyona, I had a quick chat with our Marketing Manager and as an overview, we’d initially be looking for:
Help to run our CRM (KEAP) –
to upload provided content and schedule
To handle the admin from the campaigns
To Pass on leads from campaigns and or feedback from campaigns
To Setup follow up to campaigns
To Provide the analytics for the campaigns
To Upload new contacts to CRM
To Create target groups for campaigns within CRM’s

As we progress, There will probably be more along those lines
So,  then 
Sure. Can you do 10am any day w/c June 28th? If that’s okay with you, let me know your work email and I’ll get a teams invite organised.

My email is
Pete.howard@grabbitandrun.com
June 30th at 10am U.K. would be good.
zoom preferably

Result:
Company Name: Grabbit and Run Couriers Ltd


Company Website: http://www.grabbitandrun.com


Contact Person: Pete Howard


Product:
 Theye promise we'll always receive the quality of service us deserve ... in fact they're the only courier who guarantees it ... from the degree of courtesy and politeness they show to both us and our customers ... to on-time collection and delivery. 
They are renowned for their superb quality and service standards ... a true testament to their staff and drivers. And they have one of the lowest staff and driver turnover rates in the industry, so no matter what, you get cheerful committed support from people who really do care.
They work for many blue chip organisations and SMEs .... all with a common requirement - quality, reliability, professionalism and trust.

Specialties: Same Day Courier Service, Next Day Courier Service, International Delivery, and Storage


Country-Location: UK


Target Audience: worldwide


Immediate Requirement: Pete and Andy are looking for somebody, who can manage their CRM (Data Base)  - (KEAP) - to upload provided content and schedule; To handle the admin from the campaigns; To Pass on leads from campaigns and or feedback from campaigns; To Set Up follow up to campaigns; To Provide the analytics for the campaigns; To Upload new contacts to CRM; To Create target groups for campaigns within CRM’s.
With good English language skills. 

Next Step: send all information about our company and CV’s of the most suitable candidates + SA
In future, maybe, they will need a designer

Next Contact Date:  firstly they want to look at candidates and then we will schedule an interview.

We interviewed candidates for Grabbit and Run Couriers Ltd company.
Candidates:
Alina  https://rh-s.com/marketer/lead-generation-managers/alina-bo/
LG manager. 
Elena https://rh-s.com/marketer/lead-generation-managers/elena-p/
Worked as an administrator in a hotel. Now - LG managers. 
Diana https://rh-s.com/marketer/lead-generation-managers/diana-b/
LG Manager - database.


Oksana https://rh-s.com/marketer/content-managers/oksana-m/
Can work with Wordpress, can do SMM, compains, do strategies, content plan. 



Andy and Pete said that all are good. 
But Diana likes them the most and they want to try working with her for Part Time. 
Start date - next Monday 2nd of July  + introductory call on Friday same time 9th of July.
Working hours - 12am to 4 pm (our time).  Communicative channel - Teams.

LAST FOLLOW UP EMAIL 23 09 22
